Create all Cards on Dashboard 3

Step 1: Copy District Name and Crime Group from page 2 and paste to page 3.




Step 2: Format District Name Card

                a. Select District Name Card

                b. Select formatting, in general X position = 110, Y position = 0, Width = 255, Height = 68

                c. Data label, font size = 15




Step 3: Format Crime Group Card

                a. Select Crime Group Card

                b. Select formatting, in general X position = 352, Y position = 0, Width = 301, Height = 68

                c. Data label, text size = 15




Step 4: Create Select Street Card

                a. Copy and Paste Crime Group Card

                b. Change the field to Street Level Measure

                c. Select formatting, in general X position = 609, Y position = 0, Width = 422, Height = 68

                d. Data label, text size = 26




Step 5: Create Crime Count per Day Card

                a. Field = Avg Date Diff per day

                b. Select formatting, in general X position = 1042, Y position = 0, Width = 148, Height = 68

                c. Data label, color = black, text size = 16, font = Constantia

                d. Category off

                e. Title, Crime Count per Day, color black, alignment = center, text size = 10, font = Constantia

                f. Background = light gray

               g. Border = dark gray
